    <section id="technical" class="section technical" aria-labelledby="technical-title">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="technical-title" class="section-title fade">Technical Overview</h2>
        <p class="fade" style="opacity: 0.9; text-align: center; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto 22px auto;">
          Three-phase pipeline: <strong>Dormant</strong> ‚Üí lightweight <strong>Evaluation</strong> ‚Üí <strong>Deep Processing</strong> when the significance score exceeds an adaptive threshold.
        </p>
        <div class="code-block fade" role="region" aria-label="Algorithm pseudocode" tabindex="0">
<code># Significance s ‚àà [0,1] via convex blend
s = w_m*m + w_a*a + w_c*c + w_u*u

# Gate probability (temperature œÑ)
p = 1 / (1 + exp(-(s - Œ∏)/œÑ))

# Activation decision
activate ~ Bernoulli(p)

# PI-style threshold update with energy pressure
Œ∏ ‚Üê clip(Œ∏ + k_p (p* - pÃÇ) + k_i ‚àë(p* - pÃÇ) + Œª (1 - E/E_max), Œ∏_min, Œ∏_max)</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

